Package org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.routing.database

Class LazyLoadingConnection

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.routing.database.LazyLoadingConnection
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, IConnection
public class LazyLoadingConnection extends Object implements IConnection
Provides information about the connection of a IRoadPosition. Any missing information is gathered lazy by requesting the scenario-database as soon as the respective getter method is called. Those information is cached for later calls of the same method by storing the connection from the scenario-database..

In order to retrieve more information about a connection such as start or end node, one of the following information is required at least:

  • Previous node (id) and upcoming node (id), or
  • Connection (id) and previous node (id)
